title: Analytic Symphony Series
additional-note: The latest issue of this series was have found was number 44, published in 1941.  We have found now-expired renewals for some early issues in Books volumes of the CCE, but issues might also be renewed in Music volumes, which we have not systematically surveyed, and might also be renewed under their distinctive titles, without mentioning the series title. We recommend doing copyright searches in Books and Music CCE volumes under an issue's distinctive title for any issue of this series with a copyright of 1929 or later.
